                    <img src="~/Content/Images/AboutImage4.jpg" width="854" height="480" style="border: 5px solid #ffffff; position: absolute; left: -4025px; bottom: -550px" />

                    <font color="black" face="arial" style="font-size:25px; position:absolute; left:-1000px; bottom:-585px; z-index:2; overflow:visible"> <b> ◉ Level design </b> </font>
                    <font color="black" face="arial" style="font-size:25px; position:absolute; left:-2000px; bottom:-585px; z-index:2;"> <b> ◉ C# language </b> </font>
                    <font color="black" face="arial" style="font-size:25px; position:absolute; left:-3000px; bottom:-585px; z-index:2;"> <b> ◉ 3D modelling </b> </font>
                    <font color="black" face="arial" style="font-size:25px; position:absolute; left:-4000px; bottom:-585px; z-index:2;"> <b> ◉ .NET programming </b> </font>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="width:864px; height:530px; position:absolute; background-color:white; left:1025px; bottom:-615px; opacity:0.4; z-index:-1"> </div>

